name: Inner Peace
description:
This artwork is a reassembly of the "Micro-Landscapes" collection created by TTerr.

 Each of these projects in the collection has a feeling that will be left to free interpretation. My intention was to find a way to recreate the warmth of nature and the inner peace that we all have within.

This artwork includes:

- A Peaceful Place 01
- A Peaceful Place 02
- Welcome Home

Image Size(px): 5000 x 5000
